data.description: Bask in the comfort of this clean, stylish home with abundant light and an easy living style. Premium finishes like: granite counters, high ceilings and a no wasted space vibe. Look no further for that very well cared for home in the best of locations with a community park and pool nearby. South facing makes this home a dream in the winter where the sun works in your favor. Bring your outdoor living in with big windows, covered patio, pergola, fire pit or relax in the sunshine. 3 bedrooms, office, bonus room and a garage workspace. Hang out or find your favorite space to enjoy your passion and or projects. Very low maintenance and upkeep. Move on up and enjoy this home with no back yard neighbor, nearby walking path and cul-de-sac living. Enjoy your community with events like a game a golf at our Falcon Crest Golf Course, hike in Celebration Park, float the Snake River and see some history at Swan Falls Dam. So much living to do just out your door and feel the ease of coming home to your own haven.
